These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, coffee, almond-milk, iced-tea
Sport: skiing, water-polo, skateboarding, swimming
1. Beverage:mirinda is on the right of Sport:skateboarding##1
2. Sport:swimming is on the far left##1
3. Sport:skateboarding is between Sport:water-polo and Beverage:coffee##2
4. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:almond-milk is between Beverage:coffee and Beverage:mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea         | coffee   | almond-milk | mirinda       |
| Sport      | swimming | skiing | skateboarding   | water-polo |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: skydiving, singing, writing, filmmaking
Nationality: nigerian, australian, japanese, canadian
1. Nationality:canadian is between Hobby:writing and Nationality:australian##2
2. Hobby:filmmaking is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:japanese is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
4. Hobby:skydiving is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | singing | skydiving | writing | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | australian    | canadian   | nigerian | japanese       |

