.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Food: artichoke, garlic, pear, kiwi
Nationality: german, spanish, thai, chinese
1. Nationality:thai is on the right of Food:kiwi##1
2. Nationality:thai is between Nationality:spanish and Food:garlic##2
3. Nationality:spanish is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:chinese is on the left of Food:pear##1
5. Food:garlic == Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kiwi    | artichoke | garlic   | pear  |
| Nationality   | spanish | thai   | chinese | german |

