.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
Pet: hedgehog, dog, rabbit, horse
Sport: badminton, water-polo, soccer, cycling
1. Sport:water-polo == Pet:dog##1
2. Pet:hedgehog is between Sport:badminton and Pet:horse##2
3. Sport:water-polo is on the far right##1
4. Pet:hedgehog is on the right of Sport:soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | horse   | hedgehog    | rabbit       | dog   |
| Sport   | soccer | cycling | badminton | water-polo |

